Jump Ads

Note:
	1.some site requires some script (such as jquery) from ajax.googleapis.com  or statistics script from facebook/twitter. In mainland china , you should add this sites to your proxy.I do not offer any help for this.
	2. firefox requires all host permissions to do cross-domain xhr
		example: in a.com do xhr to b.com
		you need add permission both a.com and b.com
		so for brightcove you need add all sites which using this.

